Lingua::AR::MacArabic version 0.20
================

NAME

Lingua::AR::MacArabic - transcoding between Mac OS Arabic encoding and Unicode

SYNOPSIS

    use Lingua::AR::MacArabic;

    $wchar = decodeMacArabic($octet);
    $octet = encodeMacArabic($wchar);

   # $wchar : a string in Perl's Unicode format
   # $octet : a string in MacOS Arabic encoding

DEPENDENCIES

* This module requires Perl 5.6.1 or later.
  (sorry, cannot be built with Perl 5.6.0!)

* You need a C compiler to build this module.

INSTALLATION

* At first, extract the tarball.

* Then type the following:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

